name: GALACTIC DESERT - ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE
description: GALACTIC DESERT created by an artificial intelligence running on a remote pc that uses VQGAN to create images. Each image is unique and at the same time that the AI makes a new process, it becomes more intelligent and generates better results. To create this section, the AI had to work 6 hours to generate 3000 images and select a frame for the animation of every 50 images created
